Subject: [PATCH 2076/2241] arm64: dts: a80x0: disable ihb1 AXI monitor by
 default

The AXI monitors are only used for debug purpose,
thus this patch disables ihb1 AXI monitors by default.
Whenever the debug is needed, the user can enable the
AXI monitor on demand.

